    "long_instructions": "### Make your first character's \"Walk Up\" song\r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n- Choose a character to make your first song for. Refer to your Activity Guide to determine the mood and personality of this character. \r\n- Code a sequence of sounds under `when run`. \r\n- Make sure the beginning (Measures 1-2) build up to the middle (Measures 4-6) and that leads to the ending (Measures 7-8). *Note: Your song can be longer, but do not exceed 12 measures*. \r\n- When you have a sequence you like, drag the `1 triggered immediately` block to your workspace and move all the code under `when run` to the trigger block. \r\n- Press \"Run\" and then press \"1\" on your keyboard or under the \"Run\" button to trigger your first character Walk Up song. ",
